<plot>Dal-ho never gave much thought about the value of money and lived as he pleased. However, when his father's real estate schemes backfire, Dal-ho's entire family is sent scrambling to avoid debt collectors. Mi-ran, the daughter of their largest creditor and Dal-ho's ex-girlfriend, comes up with a solution. She will pay off the family's debt if she is given exclusive ownership of Dal-ho's body.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?155852</url></doc>
